like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:03:10.000Z","msg":"其實你個比喻真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n田忌賽馬講緊<br />\n因為同grade比輸少少<br />\n所以特登用下馬黎駁人地隻上馬<br />\n下&lt;上<br />\n上&gt;中<br />\n中&gt;下<br />\n2:1 咁overall嬴"},{"pid":"6fec6e0c803ad4d312f10ad0592e8f9756ea2ab3","tid":2011021,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89475f04b38e25b9527b0ab0baf9b2c2ba5cbca9","tid":2011021,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54a238824dd6878504eea262f069b07357e2495f","tid":2011021,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e8ee9f9261871ab4e2be2a5ea27176a318ec976","tid":2011021,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"你武力夠popo?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"咁點解黃店係我哋上馬、藍店係人地下馬？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:45:39.000Z","msg":"至少而家係優勢 比起所謂set rb 燒紙皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:03:18.000Z","msg":"勇武標榜無大台<br />\n結果變成欠缺指揮既烏合之眾<br />\n各自為戰去對有統一指揮同裝備精良既黑警<br />\n所以輸係必然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃圈你可以話一樣無大台<br />\n但理念上統一啲<br />\n唔需要強大指揮<br />\n各自為政之餘又可以互相協助"},{"pid":"3a8f9b0fe5e5c01580a3e9ee9ba285f674a7d241","tid":2011021,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈既真係不可少<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以避到都盡量唔買made in china既野"},{"pid":"7baf8545140117c398f1b503e98f6e6d566314ee","tid":2011021,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"狗隊全部上馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}